      "title": "Schools to re-open on 18th July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Education has decided to grant holidays to all schools in the island from tomorrow (11) until 15th of July.",
        "The relevant decision was taken during a discussion between the education authorities, as the continued transportation difficulties which have arisen with the fuel crisis has remained as an impediment to education.",
        "The Ministry of Education announced that schools will be reopened on Monday, 18th July."
      ],
